HEADWORD: Paid
<hw>Paid</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>imp., p. p., & a.</pos> <mord>from
<er>Pay</er></mord>. <sn>1.</sn> <def>Receiving pay; compensated; hired;
<as>as, a <ex>paid</ex> attorney</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Satisfied; contented.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
⟦ldquo⟧<xex>Paid</xex> of his poverty.⟦rdquo⟧
